Damn, I should sign that petition. Like I said before: If Nintendo could get away with selling an overpriced tablet, Microsoft can do so much better.
If they would find a way to put some sort of GPU in it, have some lighter UWP gaming titles run on it and complete the trio of: Xbox, PC and portable devices, that would be brilliant.
